---
title: Mexican-Inspired Shrimp Tacos with Crunchy Coleslaw and Garlic-Lime Crema
description: You can always rely on tacos to make the family happy, and these are no exception! Tender shrimp are dredged in enchilada-style spices for a hit of smoky, aromatic flavour. A super fresh cabbage and carrot slaw adds the perfect crunch to this mouthwatering dish! Yum!
